<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="ru" lang="ru">
<head>
<meta content="text/html; charset={charset}" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
<style type="text/css">
body{font: 12px/16px Arial, Helvetica, Tahoma, sans-serif;margin: 0; padding: 0;color: #1f282c; word-wrap: break-word;background: #f6f6f6;}
.auth_desc {display: none;}
.auth_desc2 {text-align: center;font-size: 11px;font-family: Arial;padding: 15px 0px;}
.auth_pi {display: none;}
.auth_tf {background: #e6e6e5;padding: 10px;color: #686868;width: 260px;border: 0px;text-align: center;outline: none;margin: 2px 0px;}
.auth_tf:hover, .auth_tf:focus {background: #efefef;}
.auth_tf, .auth_ok, .auth_reg, .logo, .bbcodes, .balance_but, .togame_but, .post_tf, .reg_but, .comments-but, 
.lk_button, .lk_status_pay, .read_next, .bbcodes_cancel {transition: all 0.5s ease;-moz-transition: all 0.5s ease;-webkit-transition: all 0.5s ease;-o-transition: all 0.5s ease;-ms-transition: all 0.5s ease;}
.auth_ok {background: #657ca4;padding: 12px 10px 10px 10px;color: #ffffff;width: 280px;border: 0px;text-align: center;outline: none;text-transform: uppercase;margin-top: 10px;}
.auth_ok:hover {background: #5e759c;}
.auth_reg{display: none;}
.line_or{display: none;}
.login_off {background: #ffffff;border: 1px solid #ececec;padding: 5px 5px;}
.reason_off {background: #da4b3e;color: #ffffff;width: 290px;padding: 10px 5px;}
.reason_off span {text-transform: uppercase;font-weight: bold;}
.errorwrap { margin: 0 auto; width: 300px; margin-top: 16%; text-align: center; }
.errorwrap p { margin: 0 0 15px 0;}
.prof_cont {display: none;}
</style>
<title>Сайт временно отключен</title>
</head>
<body>
<div align="center" class="errorwrap">
	<p><img src="/img/logo_off.png" alt="DataLife Engine - Softnews media group" /></p>
	<div class="reason_off">Сайт временно отключен, вход</br>только для администрации.</div>
	<div class="auth_desc2">
	<b>Почему я не могу зайти?</b> {reason}
	</div>
	<div class="login_off">
	[not-group=5]
	Ждите открытия сайта. Просим прощения за доставленные неудобства. :(
	[/not-group]
	{login}
	</div>
	<br/>
</div>
</body>
</html>